{"word":"G613 - ἀποκρύπτω - apokrýptō - ap-ok-roop'-to - Hide","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποκρύπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apokrýptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ok-roop'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hide</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மறை, புதை"},{"paragraph":"to hide"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G2928 - κρύπτω - krýptō - kroop'-to/2928\">G2928</a>; to <i>conceal away</i> (that is, <i>fully</i>); figuratively to <i>keep secret:</i> - hide.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2926/2926\">G2926</a>, <a href=\"#/G2927/2927\">G2927</a>, <a href=\"#/G2928/2928\">G2928</a>, <a href=\"#/G2931/2931\">G2931</a>, <a href=\"#/G613/613\">G613</a>, <a href=\"#/G614/614\">G614</a>"}]}